  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922550/extras/b8d5ed77a6695ab4e279726e0a045152.poster.avif?t=1728221814\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922550/extras/b8d5ed77a6695ab4e279726e0a045152.webm?t=1728221814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922550/extras/b8d5ed77a6695ab4e279726e0a045152.mp4?t=1728221814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your keyboard is a level. Each key is a room on that level.</strong></h2> <br>Explore a world like no other, where your keyboard becomes a level, and each key represents a room on that level. You’ll face various logic puzzles, challenging arcade levels, cunning enemies, and unexpected surprises. Embark on an epic adventure to unravel the mysteries of this strange world, and befriend its diverse inhabitants.<br><br>With a wide variety of puzzle and arcade levels, you'll be faced with unique challenges at every turn. Experience a captivating story that boasts multiple endings, as you make critical decisions that will shape the future of this strange world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique gameplay that uses your whole keyboard to play<br></li><li>Big variety of puzzle and arcade levels<br></li><li>Captivating story with numerous endings<br></li><li>Full support of QWERTY, AZERTY and QWERTZ layouts<br></li><li>Colorblind mode</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922550/extras/b8d5ed77a6695ab4e279726e0a045152.poster.avif?t=1728221814\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922550/extras/b8d5ed77a6695ab4e279726e0a045152.webm?t=1728221814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922550/extras/b8d5ed77a6695ab4e279726e0a045152.mp4?t=1728221814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your keyboard is a level. Each key is a room on that level.</strong></h2> <br>Explore a world like no other, where your keyboard becomes a level, and each key represents a room on that level. You’ll face various logic puzzles, challenging arcade levels, cunning enemies, and unexpected surprises. Embark on an epic adventure to unravel the mysteries of this strange world, and befriend its diverse inhabitants.<br><br>With a wide variety of puzzle and arcade levels, you'll be faced with unique challenges at every turn. Experience a captivating story that boasts multiple endings, as you make critical decisions that will shape the future of this strange world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique gameplay that uses your whole keyboard to play<br></li><li>Big variety of puzzle and arcade levels<br></li><li>Captivating story with numerous endings<br></li><li>Full support of QWERTY, AZERTY and QWERTZ layouts<br></li><li>Colorblind mode</li></ul>",
